890
00:40:12,817 --> 00:40:16,367
♪The lights fade; the story isn't over♪

891
00:40:16,617 --> 00:40:20,137
♪Let's continue our fate♪

892
00:40:21,757 --> 00:40:25,727
♪A cup of wine
